 Final/intermediate sometimes depends on context.
 Financial instruments and secondhand goods are not part of GDP.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Gross
\series default
 means before subtracting depreciation (contrast with 
\series bold
net
\series default
).
